Sierra Nevada National Park, La Mucuy. Trail to Laguna Verde. Montane wet forest.

Parque National Amboró; southwest region of park, north of Comarapa; along road up to about 2 km north of pass (where GPS reading was made at 2550 m), and along ridge east of pass. Disturbed forest near road and trees and shrubs in patches along windswept ridge.

Podocarpus National Park; along maintenanace trail between the power plant of San Ramon and the communication tower on peak to the south of Cordillera del Consuelo. Route mostly follows ridge. Vegetation disturbed by trail and power line clearing.
Bajada de La Pastora a El Cedral.
EL ANGEL: Parroquia Espejo. Localidad El Voladero. Bosque Seco PreMontano. Informante: Angel Morillo.

Guaramacal National Park. Road from Bocono to Guaramacal and T.V. antenna station, near and beyond pass of main road and turnoff to T.V. antenna road up to peak. Upper montane wet forest and páramo. Forest mostly contiguous below 2850 m elev. and away from ridges, páramo generally above 2850 m elev. and continuing below this along ridges.
Monte Punco. Montane forest along and near road from Monte Punco through Parque Carasco. Area disturbed by cattle and small human settlements.
Monte Puncu-Sihuenaca road, ca. 3 km N of main highway at Monte Puncu.

Faldas al sur del Volcán Reventador. Margen izquierda del Río Reventador. Bosque huy húmedo Premontano. Bosque alterado por terremoto de 1987. Entre carretera y sendero al crater.

Cerro Golandrinas. Primary forest and vegetation highly variable due to complex topography. Mossy, upper montane pluvial forest with trees up to 30 m tall in ravines and creek bottoms. Variously stunted forest and shrubbery on exposed slopes, ridges and peaks; some areas similar to paramo.
Carretera Loja-Cuenca

Nudo de Sabanilla. Pass of road at Yangana and Valladolid province border, take trail to the east up to ridge. Disturbed upper montane forest, stunted by high winds and with more open areas of shrubs and herbs.
INTAG (finca de Carlos Zorilla), about 30 minute walk from Santa Rosa; near high pastures and ridge above with primary forest.
El Gualtal. Cresta del cerro Golondrinas Hembra. Bosque húmedo Montano Bajo. Vegetación arbustiva en la cresta de la montaña.
Parque Nacional Madidi, Keara, sector Chaquimayu, parcela permanente 32, localidad de muestreo Weinmannia 1.
